column9: Leon Black Wood Range in Inches  This attractive modern looking frame from GMGold is perfect for a wide range of settings, allowing you to display your pictures or prints in an attractive manner. Whether you need to display pictures in your home or office, our range of wooden frames are a perfect choice. We have a range of standard sizes in IN and in CM as well as A2, A3 and A4, perfect for home printed images, advertisements and posters. All frames are easy to use, with a simple system to hold your pictures in place. This makes set-up as easy as possible, and means that the picture inside the frame can be changed as frequently as you require, taking just a few minutes to make the swap with no worry about the frame being damaged from overuse.
